game.name: Barbie Pregnancy Care
game.description:
Oh girls, a great news has just come from your most favorite Barbie doll, who is going to become a mom! She is very excited and happy and seeking for someone who could help her to take care of all her needs during her last golden days of the lovely pregnancy. Her loving husband Ken is away from home and her baby bump seems to be very huge, so Barbie needs your help. Make sure that you have good medical skills to play the role of her personal super talented assistant. 

Hurry up, ladies! Join this Barbie Pregnancy Care and get ready to help your favorite doll in this brand new dressing game for girls! Check out first what she wants to eat today. Her food list includes various food items, including hamburgers, pies and cakes. Figure out first what suits her the most before making a final decision. Remember, your aim is to make her feel happy in this free online dress-up game. 

Also give her a proper smoothie. Cut the fresh fruits and put all of them into the electric blender. Pour some milk and mix them well. Keep doing the task until you get a creamy and delicious item. Relax her with a nicely chosen song in this doll dress-up game. Go through her a proper foot massage and check out her blood pressure as well as her most awaited baby heart beats in order to ensure a safe and secure pregnancy. Have a blast, kids to have the best time in this cool dress up game!
